text: Pavel Benetka (26 January 1921 - 4 May 1997) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
